{"tid":2442010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"探「鐵粉」何桂藍 黃耀明︰佢好positive","createTime":"2021-03-11T05:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T07:16:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"62b6903c7fa60b0f0cf3520cb59728a637998885","tid":2442010,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:43:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/NPGO2RL74BEURCKPL3XTF5QQGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FNPGO2RL74BEURCKPL3XTF5QQGY%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHXpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=34ded668\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FNPGO2RL74BEURCKPL3XTF5QQGY%2F&h=745774d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/NPGO2RL74BEURCKPL3XTF5QQGY/</a><br />\n<br />\n探「鐵粉」何桂藍 黃耀明︰佢好positive<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ue7trVh7FXSgL_tKo0hsnZeMbPA=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5X3Y3SGTEFBLFFUQWTUIGWC6Z4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUe7trVh7FXSgL_tKo0hsnZeMbPA%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5X3Y3SGTEFBLFFUQWTUIGWC6Z4.jpg&h=6bb82b79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃耀明昨到大欖女懲教所探望何桂藍（圓圖），稱還「人情債」。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】正在還柙的43名民主派人士身在囚牢，鬥志不滅，昨日同路人續來探望打氣，囚權組織石牆花創立人邵家臻形容各人「心靈好強大」，盼能適應獄中生活；歌手黃耀明則還「人情債」，探望「瘋狂粉絲」何桂藍；身負多宗官司的林卓廷堅拒申請私飯，堅持要習慣獄中膳食；岑敖暉則鼓勵大家「越爛嘅牌越要比心機打」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：祝君毛巾須符厚度 魷魚絲限7克裝<br />\n<br />\n下午1時許，歌手黃耀明帶同朱古力和牛肉乾等零食，到大欖女懲教所探望何桂藍。明哥指「佢仍然好positive（正面），對於自己做嘅決定。」目前被獨囚，專注寫文章消磨時間，笑言「𠵱家寫文寫到手痛」。但探訪室設備簡陋，二人隔着玻璃，僅靠電話聽筒傳來微弱聲音，「大家都好辛苦先聽到對話。」<br />\n<br />\n他解釋，何是他的多年歌迷，「佢好瘋狂㗎」，對上一次演唱會，何連續六晚捧場又送花，今次探望是還人情債，未來會繼續來探望。<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻昨到赤柱監獄探望還柙手足，因懲教探訪安排較過往繁複耗時，故未能探訪民主派人士。他透過探望民主派人士家屬得知，所有還柙的民主派人士心理質素比預期好，「佢哋心靈好強大，用自己方法去適應，去搵唔同嘅生活節奏」，令他十分鼓舞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷拒申請私飯<br />\n<br />\n身負多宗官司的林卓廷，其團隊指他被還柙後一直堅拒申請「食私飯」，稱要習慣獄中膳食，更說每餐一格白烚菜、一格白烚肉、一格飯「幾健康」，指他已從容面對。<br />\n<br />\n岑敖暉的fb專頁亦更新，指他在獄中可閱報，得知過去一周市民十分辛苦，勸勉大家「越爛嘅牌越要比心機打。」其妻Nicole發帖指已處理好並寄出第一批寫給岑的信。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席羅健熙昨到羅湖懲教所探望袁嘉蔚，他指袁在面對困難時刻，一如她腕上紋身「Fearless」一樣無所畏懼。前香港眾志常委何嘉柔探望袁後，亦惋惜早前與袁到羅湖懲教所探望周庭，豈料事隔數月卻是來探望袁感到「很諷刺」。<br />\n<br />\n沙田區議員石威廉昨到荔枝角收押所探望劉頴匡，劉提及陳日君樞機日前探望眾被告令他鼓舞，但亦擔心樞機健康，而石已向劉告知近日英超賽果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Pfjqdlt03Kk_ZMv7dVZQFyWuimY=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/47MKQCML6VBTTFFIXCLJWRBJM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPfjqdlt03Kk_ZMv7dVZQFyWuimY%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F47MKQCML6VBTTFFIXCLJWRBJM4.jpg&h=b09110f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林卓廷的團隊指他一直堅拒申請「食私飯」，稱要習慣獄中膳食。<br />\n<br />\n==========<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c049dc50a93ae1d1fcea5d10531b5ce205d5f8","tid":2442010,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d11e56518b7ba24ccc619d77fb4a273098bab3","tid":2442010,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T07:09:41.000Z","msg"